# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# YOU VS YOU — Global Environment Configuration Example
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This project uses split environment files for backend and frontend:
# - Backend environment variables go in: backend/.env
# - Frontend environment variables go in: frontend/.env.local
#
# See backend/.env.example and frontend/.env.local.example for templates.

# Shared Database & Cache settings (if running via Docker Compose)
POSTGRES_DB=YOUR_DATABASE_NAME
POSTGRES_USER=YOUR_DATABASE_USER
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=YOUR_DATABASE_PASSWORD
REDIS_URL=YOUR_REDIS_URL
